    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TaC1">
<l>cekkarmā mukiluṭuttu mikka ceñcuṭarp</l>
<l>pariticūṭi yañcuṭar matiyam pūṇṭu</l>
<l>palacuṭar puṉainta pavaḷac cevvāy</l>
<l>tikaḻpacuñ cōti marakatak kuṉṟaṅ</l>
<l>kaṭalōṉ kaimmicaik kaṇvaḷar vatupōl</l>
<l>pītaka vāṭai muṭipūṇ mutalā</l>
<l>mētaku palkala ṉaṇintu cōti</l>
<l>vāyavuṅ kaṇṇavuñ civappa mītiṭṭup</l>
<l>paccai mēṉi mikappa kaippa</l>
<l>naccuviṉaik kavartalai yaraviṉamaḷi yēṟi</l>
<l>yeṟikaṭaṉaṭuvuḷ ḷaṟituyi lamarntu</l>
<l>civaṉaya ṉintira ṉivarmuta laṉaittōr</l>
<l>teyvak kuḻāṅkaṭ kaitoḻak kiṭanta</l>
<l>tāmarai yuntit taṉipperu nāyaka</l>
<l>mūvula kaḷanta cēvaṭi yōyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Putting on big red clouds, wearing the very</l>
<l>red-glowing [sun] disk, wearing the glowing moon,</l>
<l>a coral-red mouth that is decorated with many glowing [stars],</l>
<l>an emerald hills with glittering green lustre,</l>
<l>as if sleeping in the hand of the [snake] on the ocean</l>
<l>being adorned with many eminent ornaments,</l>
<l>beginning with a golden cloth [and] a head ornament,</l>
<l>placing lustre on top so that mouth and eyes become red,</l>
<l>so that the green body is much in contrast [to them],</l>
<l>mounting the serpent bed with heads that seize troublesome karma,</l>
<l>abiding in conscious sleep in the middle of the tumultuous ocean,</l>
<l>while all the throngs of gods beginning with these: Śiva, Aja</l>
<l>[and] Indra fold [their] hands in worship,</l>
<l>o solitary great lord with a lotus navel who lies there,</l>
<l>you with red feet that measured the three worlds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
